OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FThe Government remains committed to
OL,7,Fsingle-phrase Ofsted judgments despite
OL,8,Fcalls for them to be scrapped
OL,9,Ffollowing the death of headteacher
OL,10,FRuth Perry.
OL,12,FThe Department for Education (DfE) has
OL,13,Fsaid it will "continue to listen to
OL,14,Fviews and look at alternative
OL,15,Fsystems", but it believes there are
OL,16,F"significant benefits" to headline
OL,17,Fgrades awarded in England by the
OL,18,Fschools watchdog.
