OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FIn its response to an inquiry into
OL,7,FOfsted by the Commons Education Select
OL,8,FCommittee, the DfE said the overall
OL,9,Fjudgment provides a "succinct" summary
OL,10,Ffor parents and helps identify which
OL,11,Fschools need support.
OL,13,FIt said its priority is to look for
OL,14,Fways to improve the inspection system
OL,15,Frather than "developing an alternative
OL,16,Fto it".
OL,18,FThe Government's response has been
OL,19,Fdescribed by education union leaders
OL,20,Fas "deeply disappointing" and a missed
OL,21,Fopportunity for "meaningful change".
