OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FProfessor Julia Waters, the sister of
OL,7,FMrs Perry, called the response
OL,8,F"woefully inadequate" and said the
OL,9,Fchanges offered do not go "far enough".
OL,11,FThe inspectorate has come under
OL,12,Fgreater scrutiny in the past year
OL,13,Fafter the suicide of Mrs Perry.
OL,15,FThe headteacher took her own life
OL,16,Fafter an Ofsted report downgraded her
OL,17,FCaversham Primary School in Reading
OL,18,Ffrom its highest rating,
OL,19,F"outstanding", to its lowest rating,
OL,20,F"inadequate", over safeguarding
OL,21,Fconcerns.
