OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FIn December, a coroner concluded the
OL,7,FOfsted inspection on November 15-16 in
OL,8,F2022 "contributed" to Mrs Perry's
OL,9,Fdeath.
OL,11,FA report by the Education Select
OL,12,FCommittee in January called on the DfE
OL,13,Fand Ofsted to develop an alternative
OL,14,Fto the single-word judgments "as a
OL,15,Fpriority" to better capture the
OL,16,F"complex nature of a school's
OL,17,Fperformance".
