OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FIt said as a "first step" the websites
OL,7,Fof Ofsted and the DfE should show a
OL,8,Fschool's rating in different areas,
OL,9,Fnot just the overall judgment.
OL,11,FThe DfE listed the benefits of one-
OL,12,Fword judgments in its response to MPs.
OL,14,FIt said: "So, while the Government
OL,15,Fwill continue to listen to views and
OL,16,Flook at alternative systems, including
OL,17,Fthe various approaches taken
OL,18,Finternationally, the Government's view
OL,19,Fis that there are significant benefits
OL,20,Ffrom having an Ofsted overall
OL,21,Feffectiveness grade.
