OL,6,F"In our view the priority is to look
OL,7,Ffor ways to improve the current system
OL,8,Frather than developing an alternative
OL,9,Fto it.
OL,11,F"This includes considering with Ofsted
OL,12,Fthe presentation of its findings and
OL,13,Fgrades, and opportunities to highlight
OL,14,Fsome of the detail sitting under the
OL,15,Fsummary grade."
