OL,6,FThe DfE added that it agreed with the
OL,7,Fcross-party group that part of this is
OL,8,Fabout "increasing visibility" of the
OL,9,Fgraded sub-judgments that Ofsted makes
OL,10,F` such as "quality of education" and
OL,11,F"behaviour and attitudes".
OL,13,FProf Waters, Mrs Perry's sister, said:
OL,14,F"It is depressing to see the
OL,15,FGovernment still defending aspects of
OL,16,Fthe inspection system, such as single-
OL,17,Fword judgements, that are so harmful,
OL,18,Fdivisive and counter-productive."
