OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FShe added: "The Government's response
OL,7,Fto the Education Committee's report on
OL,8,FOfsted is woefully inadequate.
OL,10,F"It is very difficult for me and my
OL,11,Ffamily to see the Government refer to
OL,12,Fmy sister by name, and then so clearly
OL,13,Ffail to respond to the many important
OL,14,Flessons from her death, that the
OL,15,Fcoroner and the Education Committee
OL,16,Fhave raised."
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@AOUxD@MO]
