OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,F"The small tweaks to the current,
OL,7,Fdangerous system that have so far been
OL,8,Foffered do not go anywhere near far
OL,9,Fenough. We need to see urgent, root-
OL,10,Fand-branch reform of this fatally
OL,11,Fflawed inspection system," she added.
OL,13,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary of
OL,14,Fschool leaders' union the NAHT, said:
OL,15,F"Single-word judgments do not 'provide
OL,16,Fsignificant benefit' ` they are deeply
OL,17,Fharmful and must be scrapped entirely.
