OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,F"Last year's tragic events showed
OL,7,Fthat, and we cannot rule out something
OL,8,Fawful happening again in future if the
OL,9,Finspectorate does not change.
OL,11,F"Should such a horrific situation
OL,12,Foccur, it will be ministers who need
OL,13,Fto answer for the decisions that have
OL,14,Fbeen taken."
OL,16,FHe said the DfE's response "smacks of
OL,17,Fa government that is out of touch with
OL,18,Fparents and professionals alike."
