PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F411A1714054875
OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,F"Its solution is to 'consider' the
OL,7,Fpresentation of Ofsted reports rather
OL,8,Fthan the system itself.
OL,10,F"This is despite all the evidence that
OL,11,Fthese single-phrase judgments are the
OL,12,Fsource of sky-high stress and anxiety,
OL,13,Fdamaging the wellbeing of leaders and
OL,14,Fteachers, sapping morale and causing
OL,15,Fmany people to leave the profession.
OL,17,F"They stigmatise schools and colleges,
OL,18,Fmaking improvement more difficult to
OL,19,Fsecure, and thus they do a disservice
OL,20,Fto children, parents and communities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
