OL,6,FLast month, Ofsted chief inspector Sir
OL,7,FMartyn Oliver launched the watchdog's
OL,8,FBig Listen public consultation which
OL,9,Fwill seek views about the inspectorate.
OL,11,FConservative MP Robin Walker, chairman
OL,12,Fof the Education Select Committee,
OL,13,Fsaid: "In recent months we have seen
OL,14,Fencouraging signs that the
OL,15,Finspectorate has listened and is
OL,16,Fwilling to change.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
