OL,6,FAn Ofsted spokesman said: "Ofsted aims
OL,7,Falways to be a force for good in this
OL,8,Fcountry, ensuring schools, children's
OL,9,Fhomes, nurseries and colleges deliver
OL,10,Fthe highest standards of education and
OL,11,Fcare to children.
OL,13,F"But we know we can improve. That is
OL,14,Fwhy we launched the Big Listen, which
OL,15,Finvites feedback from parents,
OL,16,Fprofessionals and children on
OL,17,Feverything we do."
