OL,6,FA DfE spokesperson said: "We have no
OL,7,Fplans to remove one-word judgments.
OL,8,FThey give parents the confidence in
OL,9,Fchoosing the right school for their
OL,10,Fchild and provide a clear basis for
OL,11,Ftaking action to improve
OL,12,Funderperforming schools.
OL,14,F"The Secretary of State has been clear
OL,15,Fthat we will continue to consider ways
OL,16,Fto improve the current system,
OL,17,Fincluding looking at international
OL,18,Fapproaches, and we are looking forward
OL,19,Fto hearing the views of teachers,
OL,20,Fparents and children through the Big
OL,21,FListen."
